  - ruleId: bypass_full_control_for_immediate_rescue
    title: Bypass full fire control for immediate rescue
    titleLocalizationKey: 
    triggerSummary: If victims are trapped behind smoke and still reachable, rescue may take precedence over perfect corridor control.
